<div style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 700">Stamp Cards</div>

<p>This service allows you to create and manage digital stamp cards in your retail operation.</p>

<p>Create a new stamp cards in this service, and your customer will receive an information email with a stamp card code and the number of stamps which remain until redemption.</p>
<p>The stamp card code, in the format "AA 11 22", is given to the cashier at checkout who will then redeem or add additional stamps to the digital stamp card.</p>
<p>Redeem, or verify, a stamp code by submitting the stamp card code in the service interface. Customers will receive updates by email and all the activity will be logged, trackable in your service interface.</p>
    
<p>Functions included:</p>

<ul>
<li>Create digital stamp cards with a custom amount of stamps.</li>
<li>Use and redeem stamp cards.</li>
<li>Verify status of stamp card codes.</li>
<li>Track all stamp card activities.</li>
</ul>
</div>
